paragraphs.text:
run("
SELECT orderDate,
SUM(NMIncAd) as NM,
  SUM(NMIncAd) / COUNT(DISTINCT subOrderId) AS NMBO_TOTAL
   
FROM(      
    SELECT DISTINCT atb.orderDate, atb.subOrderId, atb.deviceType, ag.sellingPrice, ue.NMIncAd
    FROM(
        SELECT DISTINCT subOrderId, orderDate, deviceType
        FROM `temp.order_sd`
        WHERE orderDate>'2023-05-04' and orderDate<'2023-05-13'
        ) atb
    JOIN(
        SELECT DISTINCT subOrderId, brand, sellingPrice
        FROM `all(agCmDump)`
        ) ag
    ON atb.subOrderId = ag.subOrderId
    LEFT JOIN(
            SELECT DISTINCT subOrderId, NMIncAd
            FROM `all(unitEconomicsBaseTable)`
            ) ue
    ON ag.subOrderId = ue.subOrderId
)
GROUP BY orderDate
",1000)
